Different files with information about how Barcelona codes its streets and gps coordinates

Streets are grouped in "itineratios" (paths)
Individual strees are divides in "trams" (segments)
http://opendata.bcn.cat/opendata/en/catalog/TRANSPORT/transitrelaciotramsperitinerari/

coordinates of Barcelona Transit cameras


Traffic info:

http://opendata.bcn.cat/opendata/en/catalog/TRANSPORT/itineraris/
http://bigovopendata.bismart.com/opendata/en/catalog/ext/TRANSPORT/trams/

Barcelona Traffic  web:

http://com-shi-va.lameva.barcelona.cat/en/traffic
